item.title: Teleport Command does not work: Help
item.dc:creator: @koopa_king koopa king
item.description:
@koopa_king wrote:

You had your player rights set so that anyone with a playerRights greater than 0 could use it. =] And yay! The problem is solved. You could have also done

if(command.startsWith("skill") && playerRights >= 0){ toX = 2845; toY = 4832; sM("Welcome to the skilling area."); }
